              Jump ARCHES Summer Internship Program at UIUC's Health Care
              Engineering Systems Center (HCESC). He worked on developing a
              virtual reality training module for Extra Corporeal Membrane
              Oxygenation (ECMO) procedures, creating an accessible simulation
              for medical professionals.
            </p><br />
