              reality developer, Suyash received the Best Business Innovation
              Award at UIUC Research Park for creating a virtual environment to
              simulate the patient screening process. His supervisor praised his
              initiative, leadership, and innovative thinking in tackling a
              project that required him to learn new technologies and
              programming languages. More recently, Suyash built an MVP prompt
              library to aid in clinical Trial document generation at AbbVie,
              leading to a $2 million contract with a consultant firm to build
              out the vision.
            </p>

